author: Augustinus Sanctus
message: The world is a book, and those who do not travel read only a page.
title: Thought of the day

author: Henri-Frederic Amiel
message: So long as a person is capable of self-renewal they are a living being.
title: Thought of the day

author: Louisa Alcott
message: I'm not afraid of storms, for I'm learning how to sail my ship.
title: Thought of the day

author: Voltaire
message: Think for yourselves and let others enjoy the privilege to do so too.
title: Thought of the day
